 23.3.18 - Red Lodg Went down to Bde . H.Q . about 11 a.m. and saw the G. who was on his way to D.H.Q . where Gener Plumer was presid at a Confer . The day was warm and close . Had a littl council of war at the Catacomb and arrang rather stronger stand and listen patrol than usual in order to cover our relief tonight better . The captur of a few men of 21st might mean that the Hun can get some inform from them regard our movement . After lunch most of the rear coy . men were taken out of their dugout and spent the afternoon sit down in the sun .
